<title>CHINA: TABLE - CHINA'S KONKA H1 NET UP 15.4 PCT.</title>
<headline>TABLE - CHINA'S KONKA H1 NET UP 15.4 PCT.</headline>
<dateline>HONG KONG 1997-08-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Six months to June 30 (in millions of yuan unless stated, against first-half 1996 figures):</p>
<p>  Turnover	     2373.01	 vs  2031.48</p>
<p>  Net profits	   164.60	 vs   142.67</p>
<p>  Earnings per share    0.45 yuan  vs     0.51 yuan</p>
<p>  Net assets per share  4.42 yuan  vs     3.30 yuan</p>
<p>Company name: Konka Group Co Ltd. The company, based in Shenzhen, is the second biggest colour television maker in China.</p>
<p>Note: The results, calculated under international accounting standards, were published in the China Securities newspaper last Saturday.</p>
<p>($1.0 = 8.3 yuan)</p>
